data.description: SELLER CONTRIBUTION TO CLOSING: $2500.00 - Don't miss this charming farmhouse-style home in the heart of McAllen! This meticulously crafted residence offers a perfect blend of modern convenience and rustic charm. Built in 2020 on a generous .2272-acre lot, this is truly exceptional property. Key Features:3 bedrooms and 2 bathrooms, providing ample space for comfortable living. Includes a spacious workshop for those with hobbies or in need of extra storage space. The home incorporates energy-efficient features to save you money while minimizing your environmental footprint. Enjoy the luxury of an extra-large primary bedroom, complete with a generous closet and double vanities. The large laundry room is both practical and stylish, with plenty of room for folding and sorting. Numerous upgrades including a tankless water heater, extra-large patio slab perfect for outdoor entertaining, security system with 6 cameras, foam insulation and double paned windows.
